## Quick Reference

```yaml
# Basic project structure
name: project-name
version: 0.1.0
workflows:
  - source: ./workflow.yaml

# Basic task structure
- id: task_name
  type: basic
  tool: tool_name
  with:
    param: "{{ .workflow.input.value }}"

# Basic agent structure
resource: agent
id: agent_name
config:
  provider: groq
  model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
```
